query: SELECT rw.id, rw.contactName, rw.rescheduledDate, r.userId, r.name as routeName FROM route_waypoints rw JOIN routes r ON rw.routeId = r.id WHERE rw.status = 'missed' AND rw.rescheduledDate IS NOT NULL;
